data.description: Don't let the 3 bedrooms fool you, this home has plenty of space to accommodate a full house or a growing family. Beautiful brick two story in desirable Fairfield Farms subdivision and Pine Forest School district. This large brick home boast 3 bedrooms, 3 full baths, a huge bonus/media room or 4th bedroom, a study and formal dining area. Hardwood floors are gorgeous, large open greatroom with vaulted ceiling, fully equipped kitchen with granite, gas range and plenty of storage space. Owners suite is downstairs with large ensuite bath with dual vanity spaces with his and hers closets, jetted tub and separate shower. First level office space off owners hall is perfect for working from home or catching up on your favorite shows. Upstairs bedrooms are spacious with ample closet space and a Jack and Jill full bath. Did we mention the 3 car garage, we have that too! All tucked in on a large corner lot with a privacy fenced backyard and covered rear patio. Don't miss this one!
